#ROOMS
#9800
@@ySunforged Causeway of Lantern@@N~
A curtain of @@llight blue@@N silk trembles between mudbrick posts and the air smells faintly of wet clay.@@N
Banners in @@llight blue@@N, @@yyellow@@N, and @@bbrown@@N mark patrol intersections and scouts can pivot quickly between side passages.@@N
To the south, an unnatural triangular ridge rises beyond the palms, promising a future road into a sealed pyramid quarter.@@N
