#9801
@@ySunforged Terrace of Mosaic@@N~
A chalky wash of @@yyellow@@N dust softens every hard edge of the lane while tiny eddies of sand curl around your boots.@@N
Interlocked tiles form an old caravan map beneath drifting sand while secondary paths reconnect after every bend.@@N
Far on the horizon, a geometric silhouette cuts the dunes where engineers whisper a pyramid gate will open one season soon.@@N
