#9802
@@ySunforged Arcade of Basin@@N~
A brace of @@bbrown@@N pylons leans toward a shaded cistern mouth as far drums pulse from another district.@@N
Reinforced berms divide this stretch into narrow tactical lanes forcing caravans to move in disciplined lines.@@N
Southward waystones stop at a barricaded arch, yet survey marks clearly continue toward a buried pyramid complex.@@N
