#9803
@@ySunforged Promenade of Canopy@@N~
A grove of date palms throws patterned shadows over old paving stones and even the heat carries a trace of mint.@@N
Cistern ladders descend through iron rings worn smooth by use and their colors match the oasis triad exactly.@@N
A distant capstone-like glimmer flashes between heat waves, foreshadowing the unopened pyramid district beyond this oasis.@@N
