#9804
@@ySunforged Crossing of Windbell@@N~
A scatter of polished shells glints where traders once sorted cargo where each footprint lingers before being erased.@@N
Merchants' awnings hang low, creating tight chokepoints as if every patrol captain signed in turn.@@N
Guard chatter mentions convoy plans for a southern pyramid dig, though the final passage remains barred today.@@N
