#9805
@@ySunforged Gallery of Survey@@N~
A low spill of water runs through chiseled channels at your feet while gulls circle far above the palms.@@N
A chain of spill basins captures every drop from northern channels and scouts can pivot quickly between side passages.@@N
Old maps etched on plaster show this corridor as the approach line to a pyramid that has not yet been connected.@@N
