#9806
@@ySunforged Passage of Saltline@@N~
A fringe of woven reed screens clicks in the dry afternoon wind and the walls hum with trapped day-warmth.@@N
Thin prayer ribbons knot from post to post above the path while secondary paths reconnect after every bend.@@N
Wind-driven sand reveals straight foundation cuts running south, hinting at the coming link to pyramid ruins.@@N
