#9807
@@ySunforged Landing of Datefire@@N~
A long bank of carved jars cools in a strip of shade as bright reflections skitter across broken glaze.@@N
Painted milestones note distances to wells and guard courts forcing caravans to move in disciplined lines.@@N
Even from here, the skyline forms precise angles no dune could make, and everyone pretends not to notice the waiting pyramid.@@N
