#9808
@@ySunforged Court of Clayrune@@N~
A line of stone braziers sits dark but meticulously swept while distant voices vanish behind shutters.@@N
Stone benches flank the route, each carved with oath marks and their colors match the oasis triad exactly.@@N
Survey stakes and chalk arrows push southward in strict geometry, outlining where a pyramid causeway will eventually run.@@N
