#9809
@@ySunforged Span of Starpool@@N~
A fan of wind-cut steps opens toward the next basin quarter and a cool draft escapes from hidden vents.@@N
A dry fountain bowl reflects the sky like a bright shield as if every patrol captain signed in turn.@@N
A blocked triumphal gate bears fresh chisels depicting a southern pyramid, clear foreshadowing of an expansion still to come.@@N
