#9840
@@yDuneshaped Causeway of Windbell@@N~
A scatter of polished shells glints where traders once sorted cargo while distant voices vanish behind shutters.@@N
Reinforced berms divide this stretch into narrow tactical lanes and scouts can pivot quickly between side passages.@@N
Survey stakes and chalk arrows push southward in strict geometry, outlining where a pyramid causeway will eventually run.@@N
